ActNational Energy Board Act
SubjectCertificate of Public Convenience and Necessity EC-13 - Hydro One Networks Inc.
PrecisOrder approving the issuance by the National Energy Board of the Amending Order AO-005-EC-13 to vary the CERTIFICATE OF PUBLIC CONVENIENCE AND NECESSITY EC-13, held by Hydro One Networks Inc., in order to change a section of Hydro One's International Power Line J5D from an overhead power line to an underground power line.
